video_title: Family is forever, drop a ❤️ if you agree #mindset #positivity #inspiration #adviceoftheday
transcript:
your children will not remember almost
any gift that you give them what they
will remember though is the memories
that you made with them the only people
in your life that will remember that you
stayed late at the office and worked
your ass off is your kids your
co-workers don't give a nobody else
cares the only people that remember that
you were at the office too much is your
children no one else cares about it so
do you want your children when they get
older to remember you as being a present
parent or being the one that was always
absent being the one that was always at
the office not being around for their
special events they won't remember the
gifts but they will remember whether or
not you were there for them
